"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"12月15日消息，金融科技初创公司CardCoins宣布通过闪电网络提供[比特币](https://www.bitcoin86.com/)支付。CardCoins是一个允许用户用预付礼品卡交换比特币的网站。该公司表示，这个新选项为用户提供了一种用现金支付比特币的快捷方式，CardCoins用户可以在美国超过80000家商店用现金购买所需的预付礼品卡。（coindesk）\",\"timestamp\":1639814917,\"title\":\"CardCoins通过闪电网络提供比特币支付\"},\"digest\":\"2xGn7avxFQsiNQtVVZYWjpvWF2Esc0dEzwuw34ongrM\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xd1C65903543DCCcD92F6F3397A1a511c1605Fa28\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"R0YJgO96hI-XvSu_US0sqPeVJMZGFuIgvOpQzUOSQ2I\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"byMHhf3DubW-PLGVvLCBhaU75C3Yekn8fctiZShbVKg\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"G9Tj_ZwtD9oJhPBWifyHCEp8Xhj8HRRYs1aPEQQX7uqt1EInUejcTVsjUUGJ3GrU59-zxY6nm1XQCSD-LMBP_g\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x772047d6d36da98e2be125d1e6aadaaf64365750eae6302f8613183e948035d2030550820726d49039e453c00b3d358eda03a49d2bad770f1fee49a93a94c5371b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"R0YJgO96hI-XvSu_US0sqPeVJMZGFuIgvOpQzUOSQ2I\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"byMHhf3DubW-PLGVvLCBhaU75C3Yekn8fctiZShbVKg\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"2xGn7avxFQsiNQtVVZYWjpvWF2Esc0dEzwuw34ongrM\"}"